msgid "主页"
msgstr "Home"

msgid "登录后进入主页，这是系统的入口，集中提供三大功能入口、传送带状态、最近检测任务与产品（PCBA）管理。"
msgstr "After login you land on the Home page — the system's entry point. It gathers the three main entries, conveyor status, recent inspection tasks, and product (PCBA) management."

msgid "主页概览"
msgstr "Home overview"

msgid "进入主页"
msgstr "Opening the Home Page"

msgid "登录系统后自动跳转至主页；在任意页面点击顶部导航栏的系统 Logo 也可返回此页面。"
msgstr "After logging in you are taken to the home page automatically; from any page you can also click the system logo in the top navigation bar to return here."

msgid "功能入口"
msgstr "Main Entries"

msgid "页面顶部为三个主要入口卡片（管理员/编程员角色可见全部三项；操作员仅可见第一项）："
msgstr "The top of the page has three main entry cards (administrators/programmers see all three; operators see only the first):"

msgid ":ui-btn:`新建检测任务`：选择一个 PCBA 开始检测（详见 :ref:`检测与反馈`）。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`New Inspection Task`: pick a PCBA and start inspecting (see :ref:`检测与反馈`)."

msgid ":ui-btn:`训练PCBA`：注册新的 PCBA / 产品并进入自动编程向导（仅管理员/编程员；详见 :ref:`创建产品`）。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Teach PCBA`: register a new PCBA / product and open the auto-programming wizard (administrators/programmers only; see :ref:`创建产品`)."

msgid ":ui-btn:`工作列表`：查看过去的检测记录与数据分析报告（详见 :ref:`查看检测历史（数据分析报告）`）。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Work List`: view past inspection records and the data analysis report (see :ref:`查看检测历史（数据分析报告）`)."

msgid "传送带状态"
msgstr "Conveyor Status"

msgid "**传送带状态** 区域显示每条传送带（如 Conveyor #A）的实时状态：:ui-opt:`空闲`、:ui-opt:`运行检测任务中` 或 :ui-opt:`定义PCB中`。常用操作："
msgstr "The **Conveyor Status** area shows each conveyor's live status (e.g. Conveyor #A): :ui-opt:`Idle`, :ui-opt:`Running Inspection`, or :ui-opt:`Defining PCB`. Common actions:"

msgid ":ui-btn:`重置轨道`：复位传送带 / 清除当前占用。仅在传送带急停（Emergency Stop）激活时生效；当出现异常占用或需要中断时使用。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Reset Track`: resets the conveyor / clears the current occupancy. Effective only when the conveyor's Emergency Stop is active; use it on abnormal occupancy or to interrupt."

msgid ":ui-btn:`刷新传送带状态`：手动刷新各传送带的最新状态。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Refresh Conveyor Status`: manually refresh each conveyor's latest status."

msgid "最近的检测任务"
msgstr "Recent Inspection Tasks"

msgid "**最近的检测任务** 列表列出最近执行的检测任务，包含以下列：任务（产品名称）、总产品数、合格率、开始时间。点击任意行可进入对应记录，便于快速回看近期生产情况。"
msgstr "The **Recent Inspection Tasks** list shows recently run inspection tasks with these columns: Task (product name), total products, pass rate, and start time. Click any row to open that record for a quick look at recent production."

msgid "产品（PCBA）管理"
msgstr "Product (PCBA) Management"

msgid "右侧 **管理PCBA** 列表展示所有已创建的产品，包含 PCBA类型、创建时间、最后更新等列。产品名称列同时显示该产品已附加的标签（Tag）。"
msgstr "The **Manage PCBA** list on the right shows all created products, with columns such as PCBA type, created time, and last updated. The product-name column also shows the tags attached to the product."

msgid "每行提供以下操作："
msgstr "Each row offers these actions:"

msgid ":ui-btn:`编辑`：进入该产品的编程页面（标记对齐、模板编辑器、拼板、整板检测等）。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Edit`: open the product's programming page (mark/align, template editor, array, whole-board inspection, etc.)."

msgid ":ui-btn:`复制`：基于现有产品创建一个副本。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Duplicate`: create a copy from an existing product."

msgid ":ui-btn:`删除`：删除该产品及其数据（需在弹出确认框中确认）。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Delete`: delete the product and its data (confirm in the dialog)."

msgid ":ui-btn:`编辑信息`：修改产品名称及标签（在弹出的编辑窗口中操作）。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Edit Info`: change the product name and tags (in the pop-up edit window)."

msgid ":ui-btn:`导出为文件`：将该产品导出为 ``.zip`` 文件，便于备份或迁移到其它机台。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Export to File`: export the product as a ``.zip`` file for backup or migration to another machine."

msgid "批量操作"
msgstr "Bulk Actions"

msgid "产品表格左侧提供复选框，可多选产品后执行批量操作："
msgstr "Checkboxes on the left of the product table let you select multiple products and run bulk actions:"

msgid ":ui-btn:`删除所选记录`：同时删除多个已选产品。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Delete Selected`: delete several selected products at once."

msgid ":ui-btn:`添加标签…`：为所有已选产品批量添加一个标签。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Add Tag…`: add one tag to all selected products at once."

msgid ":ui-btn:`移除标签…`：从所有已选产品批量移除一个标签。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Remove Tag…`: remove one tag from all selected products at once."

msgid "标签过滤与搜索"
msgstr "Tag Filter and Search"

msgid "产品列表上方提供两种过滤方式："
msgstr "Two filters are available above the product list:"

msgid ":ui-param:`按标签筛选` （多选下拉框）：同时选中多个标签时取交集过滤产品列表。"
msgstr ":ui-param:`Filter by Tag` (multi-select dropdown): selecting several tags filters the list by their intersection."

msgid ":ui-param:`搜索` （文本输入框）：按产品名称关键字过滤。"
msgstr ":ui-param:`Search` (text box): filter by a product-name keyword."

msgid "上传 PCBA 文件"
msgstr "Upload PCBA File"

msgid ":ui-btn:`上传PCBA文件(.zip)`：点击此按钮选取由“导出为文件”生成的 ``.zip`` 压缩包，将其导入为新产品；导入完成后产品列表自动刷新。若导入的产品名与系统中已有产品重名，则会提示冲突错误。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Upload PCBA File (.zip)`: click this button to pick a ``.zip`` produced by Export to File and import it as a new product; the list refreshes automatically when done. If the imported product name clashes with an existing one, a conflict error is shown."

msgid "磁盘使用情况"
msgstr "Disk Usage"

msgid "顶部导航栏右侧（全局可见，非仅限主页）显示 **磁盘使用** 微件，以环形图展示 C: 盘已用与剩余空间比例，悬停可查看具体 GB 数据。当可用空间低于 25% 时显示黄色警告，低于 10% 时显示红色严重警告并闪烁。点击刷新图标可立即重新查询。"
msgstr "The top-right of the navigation bar (visible everywhere, not just on Home) shows a **Disk Usage** widget — a ring chart of used vs. free space on C:. Hover to see the exact GB. Below 25% free it turns yellow (warning); below 10% it turns red and blinks (critical). Click the refresh icon to re-query immediately."

msgid "磁盘使用情况微件，显示 C: 容量、警示图标与刷新按钮"
msgstr "Disk Usage widget showing C: capacity, warning icon, and refresh button"

msgid "使用提示"
msgstr "Tips"

msgid "**急停状态下**：:ui-btn:`新建检测任务`、:ui-btn:`编辑` 等按钮将被禁用，需先点击 :ui-btn:`重置轨道` 恢复正常状态。"
msgstr "**Under Emergency Stop**: buttons such as :ui-btn:`New Inspection Task` and :ui-btn:`Edit` are disabled; click :ui-btn:`Reset Track` first to restore the normal state."

msgid ":ui-btn:`编辑信息` 用于修改产品名称和标签；与 :ui-btn:`编辑` 不同，后者进入产品的完整编程页面。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Edit Info` changes the product name and tags; unlike :ui-btn:`Edit`, which opens the product's full programming page."

msgid ":ui-btn:`训练PCBA` 和产品管理区域仅对 **管理员** 与 **编程员** 角色显示；**操作员** 角色只能看到新建检测任务入口与最近检测任务列表。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Teach PCBA` and the product-management area are shown only to **administrator** and **programmer** roles; the **operator** role sees only the new-inspection-task entry and the recent-tasks list."

msgid "标签（Tag）在产品行内以小徽章形式显示，可通过 :ui-btn:`编辑信息` 对单个产品修改标签，或通过批量操作同时为多个产品添加/移除标签。"
msgstr "Tags appear as small badges in the product row; change a single product's tags via :ui-btn:`Edit Info`, or add/remove tags for several products at once via bulk actions."

msgid "相关章节"
msgstr "Related chapters"

msgid ":ref:`检测与反馈` — 由 :ui-btn:`新建检测任务` 进入"
msgstr ":ref:`检测与反馈` — opened from :ui-btn:`New Inspection Task`"

msgid ":ref:`创建产品` — 由 :ui-btn:`训练PCBA` 进入"
msgstr ":ref:`创建产品` — opened from :ui-btn:`Teach PCBA`"

msgid ":ref:`查看检测历史（数据分析报告）` — 由 :ui-btn:`工作列表` 进入"
msgstr ":ref:`查看检测历史（数据分析报告）` — opened from :ui-btn:`Work List`"
